caption.body: As SFO Museum's galleries are in unconventional, always-open spaces in the Airport's terminal, we always stage our objects and test our mounts before officially installing objects. Here, life-size slot machines to be featured in an upcoming exhibition in Terminal 3 are temporarily staged in our workspace.
